==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sea thongs
<hw>Sea" thongs`</hw> <pr>(?; 115)</pr>. <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A kind
of blackish seaweed (<spn>Himanthalia lorea</spn>) found on the northern
coasts of the Atlantic. It has a thonglike forking process rising from a
top-shaped base.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Seating</ent>⟦br⟧
